00:56:39,410 --> 00:56:42,329
♫ To be able to meet our eyes just once ♫

668
00:56:42,329 --> 00:56:44,639
♫ My heart has been so transfixed ♫

669
00:56:44,639 --> 00:56:50,060
♫ I've become delirious about you, my dear ♫

