00:57:22,030 --> 00:57:25,340
Tian. Stay still!

678
00:57:25,340 --> 00:57:27,340
- Let go...
-Tian.

679
00:57:27,340 --> 00:57:29,960
Tian, stay still.

680
00:57:32,960 --> 00:57:35,700
Chief, you're scolding me again.

681
00:57:37,830 --> 00:57:41,270
You can't scold anyone else, right?

682
00:57:41,270 --> 00:57:44,200
So that's why you like to scold me instead.

683
00:57:45,040 --> 00:57:46,773
Right?

684
00:57:46,773 --> 00:57:48,413
Am I right?

685
00:57:48,950 --> 00:57:51,099
No wonder.

686
00:57:51,100 --> 00:57:54,620
That's why the Chief doesn't have a wife.

687
00:57:56,050 --> 00:57:58,219
The Chief doesn't have a wife.

688
00:57:58,220 --> 00:58:00,879
You're talking too much already.

689
00:58:00,879 --> 00:58:04,119
Who said I was scolding you? I'm smiling right now though.

690
00:58:05,630 --> 00:58:07,363
- You're smiling?
-Yeah.

691
00:58:08,370 --> 00:58:09,689
This is you smiling already?

692
00:58:09,689 --> 00:58:10,859
That's right.

693
00:58:10,859 --> 00:58:15,750
