694
00:58:17,690 --> 00:58:20,320
To smile, you gotta smile like this.

695
00:58:22,620 --> 00:58:25,359
Smile. Like this.

696
00:58:26,000 --> 00:58:27,333
No.

697
00:58:28,270 --> 00:58:34,430
Here. I'll teach you how you're supposed to smile.

698
00:58:36,840 --> 00:58:39,430
- Tian.
- Stay still.

699
00:58:40,680 --> 00:58:44,960
To smile, you smile like this.

700
00:58:59,030 --> 00:59:01,909
- Tian.
- What?

701
00:59:05,480 --> 00:59:07,530
Fine, I'll sleep then.

